{"tid":2195590,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾意左組爸/ 對他有好感","createTime":"2020-09-09T09:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T12:30:58.000Z","uid":375418,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"474be30254931d59c9da8a1833779419a0ad3877","tid":2195590,"uid":375418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:17:48.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜oday完，組爸真係好溫暖，成日照顧我地。組爸唔係好靚仔，不過好搞笑同笑得好睇，我成日都不經意咁望住佢好耐。有時候佢會望多我一眼同對著我笑<br />\n<br />\n不過有其他組女都好靚啲同外向啲，我見到組爸都會自己r 啲女仔傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ocamp完左之後成日想起他，不過又唔話題可以whatsapp<br />\n<br />\n大家有無試過同組爸發展？"},{"pid":"2f7f82294323abb001dd14ce67041f03a7db5c80","tid":2195590,"uid":183576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:18:25.000Z","msg":"約佢扑野囉"},{"pid":"8d64812f9b14f01f3b862815fa9b3532b8306b69","tid":2195590,"uid":236785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:18:54.000Z","msg":"傻閪"},{"pid":"bcbc27156808ac0a9a8f8202d55ea9b3e2ef0e1d","tid":2195590,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:19:22.000Z","msg":"愛情只是妄想症"},{"pid":"06fb4002bad31b407c5c0b0145dc3087b6923646","tid":2195590,"uid":310700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:19:23.000Z","msg":"Gay<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760636faa6d94a12cb0b49169841b2a69098e1d7","tid":2195590,"uid":372221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:19:38.000Z","msg":"佢可能對個個都係咁啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f72917ea9ffaf886fa331e6f125aa99d6dc303","tid":2195590,"uid":303464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:20:33.000Z","msg":"潮文召喚"},{"pid":"d0a83cb6e96677e207a780c0f